longBusinessSummary: Vertiseit AB (publ), a retail tech company, operates digital in-store platform in Europe. It operates through SaaS, Consulting, and Systems segments. The company provides Grassfish and Dise in-store experience management Software as a Service (SaaS) platforms. The company was incorporated in 2008 and is headquartered in Varberg, Sweden.
